// To add a server:
//   1. Uncomment and configure the desired block below
//   2. Reload VS Code (Ctrl+Shift+P → "Developer: Reload Window")
//   3. The server's tools become available to Copilot agents automatically
//
// Secrets: reference environment variables using ${ENV_VAR_NAME} syntax.
// Never put actual tokens or keys in this file.
